		<description><![CDATA[Hopes rise and dreams flicker and die. Love plans for tomorrow and loneliness thinks of yesterday. Life is beautiful and living is pain. The sound of music floats down a dark street. Hunter S. Thompson]]></description>
				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Hopes rise and dreams flicker and die. Love plans for tomorrow and loneliness thinks of yesterday. Life is beautiful and living is pain. The sound of music floats down a dark street.</p>
<p style="padding-left: 300px;">Hunter S. Thompson</p>
